AG and/or its subsidiaries in the U.S. and other) show

/y y 7 sub def

x2 y moveto

(countries. ITC Avant Garde Gothic, ITC Bookman, ITC Zapf Chancery

and ITC Zapf Dingbats are registered) show

/y y 7 sub def

x2 y moveto 

(trademarks of International Typeface Corporation in the U.S. and

other countries.) show

showpage


(HP LaserJet IID) product eq (HP LaserJet IIID) product eq or

{resetduplextrue setduplexmode} if


